ICandelo loMphathiswa eli lilo eliya kuphendula kurhulumente ngemisebenzi eyenziweyo liSebe kwanangeenkonzo ezinikiweyo kuMphathiswa osesikhundleni. Iya kuba lilo eliseka umgaqo-nkqubo lihlenga-hlengise nomthetho ngokomyalelo onikwe uMphathiswa, kwanokukhangela ukuphunyezwa kweeprojkethi eziqinisekisa ukunika ingxelo nokujongana noxanduva malunga nokusetyenziswa kwemali yorhulumente
